div.head: Description of changes for 2012.08
div.p: This is the first public version of this text. It is a first draft copied over from the diplomatic transcription of the St. Victor text. Corrections and additions will be made after a collation comparision of manuscript witnesses. Citations, cross-references, and critical appartus still need to be constructed.
